dc_description_s: This data represents streets for the City of Milwaukee, Wisconsin in 2020. [Contains a graphic representation of the street center line as well as attribute data for each official street including address ranges, street direction, street name and street type. Although most dime segments fall near the center of the right-of-way, it is not an accurate representation of street center lines. It is a tool for obtaining street name and address information for streets within the city of Milwaukee.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data, please visit: https://data.milwaukee.gov/dataset/streets
